## Functional Requirements

- User Authentication  
- Student Registration  
- Course Enrollment  
- Attendance Management  
- Grade Management  
- Time Table Management  
- Notifications/Announcements  
- Report Generation  
- Fee Management  
- Profile Management  

## Non-Functional Requirements

- Performance  
- Scalability  
- Security  
- Availability  
- Usability  
- Portability  
- Maintainability  
- Backup & Recovery  
- Localization  
- Responsiveness  
